Israel, Hamas in Indirect Contact on Violence, Israel Radio Says

-- B y   G w e n   A c k e r m a n
-- 
2011-04-10T10:45:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-10/israel-hamas-in-indirect-contact-on-violence-israel-radio-says.html
Israel  and the Islamic militant
Hamas group that rules the Gaza Strip are holding indirect
contacts through European countries and United Nation officials
in an attempt to haly escalating violence, Israel Radio said,
citing remarks by Army Spokesman Brigidier General Yoav
